<p>Because we expect you to collect four copies of everything, each deck includes 27 checklist cards, one for every card on the Reserved List. Customize your Challenger deck to your heart&#8217;s desire, or collect all 2,268 and complete your set! If you have enough checklist cards, you have a Legacy deck.</p>
