				<description><![CDATA[Call on the power of the moon and control the game with this collection of essential Mountains, now with a stunning new look.

Each <em>Signature Spellbook: Blood Moon</em> will contain nine cards: eight cards and a foil version of one of those eight cards at random.]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><center><br />
<strong style="font-size: 300%;">PURCHASE THIS PRODUCT</strong><br />
<strong style="font-size: 200%;">APRIL 1st, 2018 | #MTGBLOODMOON</strong></p>
